headline: 3 Big Reasons to Love AutoZone (AZO)
summary: Although AutoZone (currently trading at $4,028 per share) has gained 12.9% over the last six months, it has trailed the S&P 500’s 26.5% return during that period. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
